quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,And the warners have certainly come to Pharaoh’s people
  54,42,"They denied all Our signs, so We took them (into punishment), a powerful and awesome taking"
  54,43,"Are your disbelievers better than them, or is there immunity for you in the scriptures"
  54,44,Or do they say we are united and victorious
  54,45,They are all going to be defeated and turn their backs (running away)
  54,46,"No, the hour is their appointment time, and the hour is more awful and bitterer (than this world’s punishment)"
  54,47,Indeed the guilty ones are in error and madness
  54,48,"A day when they are dragged into the fire on their faces (they are told): taste the touch of hell"
  54,49,Indeed We created everything in correct proportion
  54,50,"And Our command is only once, like a blink of an eye"
  54,51,"And We have certainly destroyed your kinds, so does anyone take notice"
  54,52,And everything they did is in the books
  54,53,And everything small or big is written
  54,54,And indeed those who control themselves will be in gardens and rivers
  54,55,"In a seat of truth, with a mighty ruler"